column2: SELECT TOP # gsl.oiii_#_flux, gsl.oiii_#_flux_err, gsl.nii_#_flux, gsl.nii_#_flux_err, gsl.h_alpha_flux, gsl.h_alpha_flux_err, gsl.h_beta_flux, gsl.h_beta_flux_err, p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_z, p.dered_r, p.dered_g FROM Galaxy as p JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON p.specobjid = gsl.specobjid WHERE gsl.oiii_#_flux > # AND gsl.nii_#_flux > # AND gsl.h_alpha_flux > # AND gsl.h_beta_flux > #
